Adds keyboard shortcuts to HubSpot for chromium-based browsers.

Install from [Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/hubspot-keyboard-shortcut/khnbcanbcolodegbjmmbfnmbgnlnjcce)

